#compdef emqtt
# Documentation: source-direct extraction from upstream
# emqx/emqtt src/emqtt_cli.erl (**Erlang language**;
# uses `getopt:parse` library â€” jcomellas/getopt; first
# documented Erlang getopt:parse CLI in the corpus):
#   src/emqtt_cli.erl lines 26-29
#     (`-define(HELP_OPT, [{help, undefined, "help",
